ntence\": \"These are happy tears.\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"happy tears\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are willing to put yourself on the line every single time, I think there is no such thing as a loss.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"no such thing\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"a loss\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so happy the right man won.\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right man\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not defining myself by a medal.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I define myself by my heart and what it has made me feel and produce.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's got the best out of me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This sport has broken me, but it's also given me life, it's given me everything I am and I am happy to stand here with not really any answers to what that performance is but a happy heart and that is all that matters.\\\"\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This sport\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"not really any answers\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"that performance\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"a happy heart\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty then shared his son's reaction to the news.\"